OL,6,FA paedophile has been jailed for 24
OL,7,Fyears after carrying out serious
OL,8,Fsexual offences against a six-year-old
OL,9,Fand eight-year-old boy.
OL,11,FAndrew Thomson, 53, groomed his first
OL,12,Ftwo victims, attempted to rape them
OL,13,Fand carried out multiple sexual
OL,14,Fassaults against them. He also forced
OL,15,Fthem to watch him perform lewd acts on
OL,16,Fhimself in their presence.
OL,18,FThomson told his victims not to tell
OL,19,Fanyone about what he was doing to them
OL,20,F'or it will be bad luck in life'.
